(768, 1, 'Fall 2019', 'Clinical and Social Sciences in Psychology', '21663', 'CSP 267', 'PSYCHOLOGY OF GENDER', 4, 5, 'Exploration of the ways males and females differ in interaction, theories of development of sex differences, consequences for social change.', 'No prerequisite specified'),
