(773, 1, 'Fall 2019', 'Clinical and Social Sciences in Psychology', '21717', 'CSP 289', 'DEVELOPMENTAL CHILD PSYCHOPATHOLOGY', 4, 5, 'Presents theory, research, assessment, and intervention in child and adolescent psychological disorder. Contributions of the normal developmental perspective to understanding psychopathology and risk, and vice versa, are emphasized.', 'PSY 101'),
