(2116, 1, 'Fall 2019', 'Psychology', '40442', 'PSY 351', 'RESEARCH IN DEVELOPMENT NEUROPSYCHOLOGY', 4, 5, 'This course provides guided, direct research experiences in developmental neuropsychology, with a particular focus on autism and other developmental disabilities.', 'No prerequisite specified'),
